create a "screensaver" folder in /mnt/onboard/.kobo

set to never auto shutdown timer

set to 5 minutes the auto sleep timer

toggle on library autoupdates at a certain time of day 

install KoboStuff package by niluje

	toggle devmodeon by searching "devmodeon" in searchbar

	toggle on wifi always on in developer options

update the stuff-daemons.sh in your folder
/usr/local/stuff/bin/




